<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zài shì jiè de měi yī gè jiǎo luò dōu yǒu wǒ zuì qīn ài de tóng bāo,
 wǒ wèi nǐ zhù fú yuàn shén yǒng ài nǐ wǒ men bǐ cǐ qí dǎo,
 dàn yǒu rén què hū lüè le liáng shàn, wàng jì rèn shì yé hé huá de míng,
 rú liú làng ér zài wài miàn piào pō bù zhī dào huí jiā,
 qǐng nǐ zhēng kāi yǎn, qǐng nǐ zhēng kāi yǎn, shì jiè měi tiān zài biàn huà,
 dōu zài zhǔ shǒu zhōng, bù yào zài liú làng, wǒ men yī qǐ huí jiā.</lyrics>
<title>zài shì jiè de měi yī gè jiǎo luò 迦南209</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
